author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Pop the Champagne, ladies and gents, because Kathleen Kennedy is leaving Lucasfilm. Sure, she leaves a trail of broken franchises in her wake that will never fully recover, but I'm sure it was all worth it to push The Message. Join me, MauLer, Nerdrotic, Snarky Jay and Angry Badger for a little celebration stream. 

Sub to Nerdrotic: https://www.youtube.com/@nerdrotic
Sub to Snarky: https://www.youtube.com/@snarkyjay
Sub to Badger: https://www.youtube.com/@TheAngryBadger3
title: Open Bar #132 - Kennedy Out, Andor Season 2, Feige Done At Marvel?
